            <div class="title">
                Palestine (Jewish Terrorism)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-01-31/debates/7cc6bb64-0760-4a60-8556-f17f45c4f96a/ShipRepairingPortOfLondon" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
