            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e882210a-e115-4c17-a490-bbc504d9d4f7">
                Mr. Crossman  (Coventry, East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e882210a-e115-4c17-a490-bbc504d9d4f7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-31/debates/95d0e71b-ae3a-4509-81be-be17f353608e/Palestine(JewishTerrorism)#contribution-e882210a-e115-4c17-a490-bbc504d9d4f7">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
