            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ca59c81a-7a70-4386-bfc3-3cb041dfd578">
                Mr. Gammans  (Hornsey)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ca59c81a-7a70-4386-bfc3-3cb041dfd578" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
