<p class="">It was a bomb containing leaflets.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-05da0d83-951b-4143-bd5b-9e3f4ef1b96d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
